                    <h3>Interactive Lessons</h3>
                    <p>
                        Forget passive videos. Write real code right on your
                        phone with our custom-built mobile IDE.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card fade-up">
                    <div class="feature-icon green">
